    "statement": "Octelium is a free and open source, self-hosted, unified zero trust secure access platform that is flexible enough to operate as a modern zero-config remote access VPN, a comprehensive Zero Trust Network Access (ZTNA)/BeyondCorp platform, an ngrok/Cloudflare Tunnel alternative, an API gateway, an AI/LLM gateway, a scalable infrastructure for access and deployment to build MCP gateways and A2A architectures/meshes, a PaaS-like platform, a Kubernetes gateway/ingress and even as a homelab infrastructure.",
